 DEVELOPMENT OF CLINDATA, A CLINICAL TRIAL DATA MANAGEMENT SYSTEM.DESCRIBES THE DESIGN AND IMPLEMENTATION OF A CLINICAL TRIAL DATA MANAGEMENTSYSTEM AT THE WELLCOME RESEARCH LABORATORIES. BASED ON AN IBM 3031 COMPUTER,THE SYSTEM PROVIDES THE CAPABILITY FOR ON-LINE DATA INPUT, SEARCHING ANDCOMPREHENSIVE DATA ANALYSIS. THE DATA BASE ALSO PERFORMS AN ADVERSE REACTIONREPORTING FUNCTION AND PROVIDES FOR LONG TERM FOLLOW-UP OF PATIENTS